{"tid":2175892,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【教育淪陷】初中生活與社會及通識教科書 警噴椒持棍打壓示威漫畫被消失","createTime":"2020-08-26T17:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T18:55:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1be96e79595837380354e1863bd30428472daf31","tid":2175892,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:54:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/JHFFSODEXVDQZELWL4URM42STU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FJHFFSODEXVDQZELWL4URM42STU%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=44e87f42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FJHFFSODEXVDQZELWL4URM42STU%2F&h=634f2e92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/JHFFSODEXVDQZELWL4URM42STU/</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局透過「自願送審」機制大幅「河蟹」高中通識教科書，《蘋果》發現，初中通識科以至生活與社會科（生社科）的教科書都不能倖免。有生社科教科書在今年的「重印兼訂正」版本中，刪去警察向示威者噴胡椒噴霧的漫畫，又將普選的意義由「提升市民對本地的認同」改為「提升市民對香港特區的認同」。有書商指出，「重印兼訂正」一般只會改錯處而不會改換用詞。有通識科教師認為，相關資料明顯因觸犯政府禁忌而被刪，刻意迴避事實。"},{"pid":"3534674215fc192ed3b8a364ac087de7ae28989e","tid":2175892,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:56:44.000Z","msg":"跗蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"c599ff2c15aabadf136dd3cb8976317aa6cbc7ad","tid":2175892,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"學 習語錄 指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8369378d4c6bc09d30ff17c8f841220cefc6eb51","tid":2175892,"uid":287751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:55:33.000Z","msg":"教育的崩潰足以摧毁一個國家。<br />\n<p class=\"right\">- 曼德拉</p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>借個位 請幫推<br />\n831 有行動</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">【行動 Post 請置頂】八三一週年，手足歸隊啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2175581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2175581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">827 著黑衫</span><br />\n<span class=\"green\">906 九龍見</span></span>"}]}